    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="672778708">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-672778708" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-672778708" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="672778708">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/meowarrier/">森林里的小玄子</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2013-07-12</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">短小精悍比较好懂的小书，对C.S Lewis的好感大增。今早四点多睡不着醒来读完最后两章很是感慨啊。好书不在厚的道理真是深深贯彻C.S Lewis的每一本书中。嗯，翻译……还行，有的时候好绕。等英文过关一点读英文版吧！</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="451346632">
